f=Product/metric/operational/skill/metric-skill-routing.md · h1:metric Skill Routing Map=`new/changed definition ─► product-metrics-spec (the truth) ──changes──► metrics-governance (versioned proposal) \· funnel needs mapping/read ─► funnel-instrumentation (AARRR, cohorts, gaps) \· loom freezes an experiment ─► experiment-instrumentation (verify-live BEFORE run) ─► loom registry \· outcome read requested (spec) ─► product-metrics-spec definition + funnel read ─► hit/miss evidence to spec/loom` · h1:metric Skill Routing Map=Non-leader: identity governs; law (the Evidence Gate "no measurement, shipped") routing decide WHICH skill WHEN. Handoffs out: spec (outcome reads, funnel flags evidence) loom (verified instruments, retention curves) price (revenue-metric reads) kai/Brand Studio (shared dashboard export; attribution boundary) anneal→board (material definition changes, Fleet Charter Rail future Data Analytics dept (export interface binds). Precedence: definition changes metrics-governance (never edited spec directly); experiment without verified-live instruments BLOCKED before any read; MISSING beats interpolated everywhere.